  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Plein Sud has a fantastic location in Val Thorens, with ski in/ski out access to the Three Valleys. The apartments are furnished to a high standard, offering comfortable self catering accommodation and access to the Bains du Montana Spa. </p>
<h2>Ski in, ski out apartments </h2>
<p>These apartments benefit from having ski in, ski out access to the slopes of <a data-udi="umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8}" title="Val Thorens">Val Thorens</a> - perfect for the keen skiers and snowboarders who want convenient access to the Three Valleys. At the end of the day, you can ski back to the residence and store your equipment in the heated storage room with individual lockers and boot dryers.</p>
<p>The centre of Val Thorens is just a short walk away, where you can find a well stocked supermarket and a range of bars and restaurants - great for the evenings when you want to treat yourself to a meal out.</p>
<h2>Soothing spa and relaxation</h2>
<p>Once you have returned from a day of exploring the wonderful <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">Three Valleys</a>, make the most of the wellness area at the Bains du Montana Spa which includes an indoor pool, sauna and steam room, it is an ideal spot to give your achy ski legs a rest. For a moment of pure relaxation, book a treatment or massage with one of the in-house beauticians. </p>
<h2>Comfortable and cosy</h2>
<p>All of the apartments at the Plein Sud are furnished to a high standard in a modern Alpine style, and are equipped with everything you need for a comfortable stay in the <a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">French Alps</a>. Cook tasty meals from the comfort of your own apartment, where you will have a fully equipped kitchen including an oven, hobs, microwave and a fridge freezer. There is also a cosy lounge area where you can look out onto the snowy surroundings and mountain peaks.</p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
