  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Two bedroom apartments </strong>sleep two to four people and are between 55m². The apartments have an open plan living room and kitchenette, balcony, one double bedroom with an en-suite bathroom with a shower room and one twin bedroom, with the main bathroom having a bath.</p>
<p><strong>Three bedroom apartments </strong>sleep four to six people and are between 75m² . These apartments have an open plan living room and kitchenette, balcony, one double bedroom with an en-suite shower room, and two twin bedrooms with en-suites (one with a bath).</p>
<p>Beds are made on arrival, a mid week towel change is available on request and end of stay cleaning is included with the exception of the kitchen and bins, which must be taken out.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type: none;">
<ul>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Balcony with mountain views</li>
<li>Kitchenette, oven, hob, microwave, fridge, freezer, dishwasher, toaster, kitchenware, kettle, tea and coffee making facilities including a Nespresso coffee machine (pods not provided)</li>
<li>Bath robes and slippers</li>
<li>Towels (changed mid week)</li>
<li>Bed Linen</li>
<li>Bath or shower room</li>
<li>Satellite TV with English speaking channels</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Telephone</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Toiletries</li>
<li>Cleaning kit</li>
<li> Additional beds are available for a supplement</li>
<li>Baby cots are available (on request). Free for children under 2 years old.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
